_aChangeLog.text: Fixes some sound's that were missing and added alitle reverb to the firing sound's making them more dynamic sounding inside or outside

_sText:
-CSS MW2 Secondwind Pack-

Video Preview: https://youtu.be/isXv6gqq0rU

---I USED NO PORTED MATERIAL'S---
I do no like ripping ppl off from their work, I know the feeling...
specially sound's, I'm very picky when it come's to this issue so I prefer making my own. If I intend on useing someone's sound file's "more then likely not" I'll give the credit as alway's. Another note, I myself changed little thing's around in this pack just for my liking but I wasnt about to, dig through every little file, number, and letter to put the credit's down... I don't care about the pidley thing's. I think a couple of the physic's sound's are Valve's.

Mainmenu / Loading Screen: Secondwind

secondwind (c) sounds 2018 - "Reload sound's, Physic's except for a couple, Player sound's, etc"

"Under is the rest of the creditinals"

Inifityward, Aspyr (c) 2009 Firing sound's / Radio sound's / Music "Firing, radio, music - All edited by secondwind"
